data.description: This move-in-ready home is a must-see! Located in a secret, family-friendly Saint Clair Shores neighborhood with minimal traffic, you will find this beautifully updated three-bedroom brick ranch. The hardwood floors are original and well-maintained. The fully renovated main bathroom features a custom-built cabinet with a stunning granite countertop. The fully renovated half bath is cozy yet feels luxurious. The partially finished basement is a great entertainment spot, leaving plenty of room for guests or your home office. The backyard is lovely in the spring and summer with trees that create more privacy. As a bonus, it is already prepped for a pool, which can be included if you like.   New central air in 2023. Hot water heater was replaced in 2017. Bedroom, bathroom, and kitchen windows replaced and under transferable warranty. All existing appliances are included.
